Location


















Snyder‚Äôs-Lance, Inc.



Public
Consumer Products
Manufacturing
Food
5,000 - 10,000 Employees
181 Active Jobs





Snyder‚Äôs-Lance, Inc., headquartered in Charlotte, NC, manufactures and markets snack foods throughout the United States and internationally. The Company‚Äôs products include pretzels, sandwich crackers, potato chips, cookies, tortilla chips, restaurant style crackers, nuts and other snacks. Snyder‚Äôs-Lance has manufacturing facilities in North Carolina, Pennsylvania, Iowa, Indiana, Georgia, Arizona, Massachusetts, Texas, Florida, Ohio, and Ontario, Canada. Products are sold under the Snyder‚Äôs of Hanover, Lance, Cape Cod, Krunchers!, Tom‚Äôs, Archway, Jays, Stella D‚Äôoro, O-Ke-Doke, and Grande brand names along with a number of private label and third party brands. Products are distributed nationally through grocery and mass merchandisers, convenience stores, club stores, food service outlets and other channels. The Company Snyder‚Äôs-Lance Inc. was formed by bringing the best of two companies together in Snyder‚Äôs of Hanover and Lance Inc. in December 2010. 





Benefits
Find your satisfying career with us.
We're known for some of America's favorite snack foods, but the ingredients that make us special are our people. Lance Inc. offers enriching career opportunities fortified with the strength and stability of an organization that values its employees.
Join us, and get a taste for Snyder's-Lance Inc.






Values
Snyder's-Lance Inc. is a values-based company, firm in our beliefs and dedicated to incorporating them into everything we do. Our values form the foundation of our company and guide the behaviors of our leaders and our employees.





Employee Benefits
Our benefits are made from only quality ingredients.We strive to offer all of our employees the most attractive benefits packages available while being mindful of our obligation to create a healthy work.life.balance.Benefit PlansExclusive Provider Organization (EPO), Participating Provider Option (PPO) or High Deductible Health Plan (HDHP) with Prescription Coverage
Dental Coverage 
Vision Coverage 
Voluntary Cancer Coverage 
Flexible Spending Accounts Health Savings Account 
Basic and Supplemental Life Insurance Accidental Death & Dismemberment Coverage 
Disability Coverage 
Employee Assistance Programs 
