401(k) and Roth 401(k) Savings Plan 401(k) Catchup and Roth 401(k) Catchup Plans
Profit Sharing Plan
 Stock PlanEmployee Stock Purchase Plan (ESPP)





Culture
It takes many unique flavor combinations to create our cracker sandwiches, but only a few special ingredients make a great career.
Satisfying America's appetite is no small feat. We succeed with a unique pride in our products and our people.
Corporate
Our corporate headquarters is located in Charlotte, North Carolina where we house Professional and Executive Leadership in the following departments: Sales & Marketing, Human Resources, Finance & Accounting, Supply Chain, Information Technology & Strategic Initiatives.
This location supports the centralized operations that, in turn, support our various manufacturing facilities and the sales and distribution of our snack food products throughout much of the United States and other parts of North America. Career opportunities in this location highlight professional opportunities in various functional disciplines.
Opportunities include:
Accounting & Payroll
Administrative
Brand Management/Category Management
Sales & Marketing
Human Resources
Information (SP) Technology
Leadership
Internship Programs
Supply Chain
At Lance Inc., our supply chain drives a system of people, technology, activities, information and resources involved in moving a product from our manufacturing facilities to our customers. Our supply chain organization focuses on driving activities to transform natural resources, raw materials and components into a finished product that is delivered to the end customer. This area of our business focuses on logistics, manufacturing, procurement and distribution.
Opportunities include:

Purchasing
Logistics
Manufacturing Management
Leadership
Maintenance
Continuous Improvement
Engineering
Sales
The Lance sales organization focuses on driving sales of our private label products. Our sales & marketing department values developing and maintaining solid customer partnerships, contributing as a team, and applying innovation to drive business results.
Opportunities include:
Sales and Marketing
Leadership
Field Sales
Zone Sales Analyst
Market Specialist
Operations Management
Zone Business Management
Area Sales Leaders
Route Sales Representatives






